<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body>
        <h2>HTML FORMS</h2>
        <form action="/server_submit.php">
            <label for="first name">first name:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="first name" name="first name"><br><br>
            <label for="last name">last name:</label><br>
            <input type="text" id="last name" name="last name"><br><br>
            <input type="submit" value="Submit">
        </form>
        <p>If you can click the "submit" button, the form-data will be sent to a page called"/server_submit.php".</p>
    </body>
</html>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body>
        <h2>The select (Dropdown)Element</h2>
        <p>The select element defines a dropdown list</p>
        <form action="/action_page.php
        <label for="cars">choose a car</label>
        <select id="cars"name="cars">
            <option value="gm">GM</option>
            <option value"chevy">chevy</option>
            <option value="ford">Ford</option>
            <option value="chrysler">Chrysler</option>
            </select><br><br>
            <input type="submit">
            </form>
    </body>
</html>
!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body>
        <h2>Radio Buttons</h2>
        <p>The <strong>input type="radio"</strong> defines a radio button:</p>
        <p>Choose your favorite web language:</p>
        <form action="/action_page.php
        <input type="radio" id="html" name="fav_language" value="HTML">
        <label for="html">HTML</label><br>
        <input type="radio" id="css" name="fav_language" value="CSS">
        <label for="css">CSS</label><br>
        <input type="radio" id="javascript" name="fav_language" value="JavaScript">
        <label for="html">HTML</label><br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="submit">
        </form>
    </body>
</html>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body>
        <h2>Checkboxes</h2>
        <p>The <strong>input type="checkbox"</strong> defines a checkbox:</p>
        <p>Choose your favorite web language:</p>
        <form action="/action_page.php
        <input type="checkbox" id="html" name="fav_language" value="HTML">
        <label for="html">HTML</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="css" name="fav_language" value="CSS">
        <label for="css">CSS</label><br>
        <input type="checkbox" id="javascript" name="fav_language" value="JavaScript">
        <label for="html">HTML</label><br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="submit">
        </form>
    </body>
</html>
</html><!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <body>
        <h2>Date field</h2>
        <p>The <strong>input date="Date"</strong> is used for input fields that should contain a date.</p>
        <form action="/action_page.php
        <label for="birthday">Birthday:</label><br>
        <input type="date" id="birthday" name="birthday"><br><br>
        <input type="submit" value="submit">
        </form>
        <p><strong>input date="date"</strong>is not supported in Internet Explore 11 or prior,safari 14.1</p>
    </body>
</html>
